    <div class="prose">
      <p>Every contractor who runs multiple service trucks has experienced the same failure mode: a van breaks down mid-week, a job gets rescheduled, the client complains, and the mechanic's bill runs four figures. FleetSafe Pro eliminates that by centralizing vehicle maintenance tracking, inspection scheduling, fuel logging, and repair history into a single dashboard that every driver can access from their phone.</p>

      <p>This guide walks through setting up FleetSafe Pro for your contracting fleet — from initial configuration to driver check-in procedures — so your trucks stay on the road and off the lift. The entire setup takes under 30 minutes.</p>

      <h2>What FleetSafe Pro Does for Contractors</h2>
      <p>FleetSafe Pro is a <strong>vehicle fleet management platform</strong> designed for small-to-medium trade businesses that run 2–50 service vehicles. It replaces sticky-note reminders, spreadsheet maintenance logs, and the "check the oil when you remember it" approach that leads to breakdowns at the worst possible moment.</p>

      <table>
        <thead>
